## Additional Terms for Educational and Research Use

This project is developed as part of the UPC Esperanza educational initiative
to democratize communication through technology. 

### Educational Use
- This software is provided free for educational purposes
- Students and researchers are encouraged to build upon this work
- Please cite this project in academic work if used as a reference

### Data and Model Usage
- The included trained models and data are provided for research purposes
- Commercial use of the models requires explicit permission
- The training data represents volunteer contributions for the advancement of
  sign language recognition technology

### Citation
If you use this work in academic research, please cite:
```
LSP Esperanza (2025). Real-time Sign Language Translation System with 
Bidirectional GRU. UPC Esperanza Project. 
GitHub: https://github.com/Jaed69/Salvacion
```

